from\": 1617, \"to\": 1655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He toldMorning Reporthe was definitely aiming for a sixth games in Los Angeles in 2028.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999045031, \"rank\": 8.892803993837657e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Reporthe\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"a sixth games\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there is a lot of room to go, especially in the long jump, I think there is a lot of technical changes and perfection I can do.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"room\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"technical changes\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously the 400, I think there is a lot of gains to be made there, today I ran a PB but I wasn't that fresh, and so, I am actually really excited for the next four years,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"score\": 0.9999999936940185, \"rank\": 6.098509565962213e-09, \"text\": \"PB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"gains\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the next four years\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was happy with